description:
This is a 9 minute workout called '8 Minute Stretching Routine For People Who AREN’T Flexible!' from the channel Tone and Tighten.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Follow-along total-body stretching routine to decrease tightness and improve flexibility! Dr Jared Beckstrand leads you through 8 minutes of stretching exercises that are perfect for beginners, after a workout, or if you generally feel “tight” or “stiff”!

===========================
➡️ LINK TO DR JARED’S THICK EXERCISE MAT: https://urlgeni.us/amzn/drjaredexercisemat

➡️ LINK TO DR JARED’S STRETCH OUT STRAP: https://urlgeni.us/amzn/stretchoutstrap
===========================

Have you ever searched for “stretching routines” or “stretching exercises” here on YouTube?

I mean - I understand the importance of stretching as well as anybody, but I don’t feel like you should have to be a yoga master to do it and enjoy it!

Even some of the “beginner” routines out there are way too complex!

That’s why in this video I wanted to share with you a simple-to-follow 8-minute stretching routine that ANYONE can do at home to improve overall flexibility and mobility.
